.SH Version 3.1.0 (2012\-02\-06)
.PP
Minor:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Added \fB\fCbinman help\fR command for use by non\-Ruby bin scripts.  See README
for usage examples from Perl, Python, Node.js, Tcl, AWK, and UNIX shell!
.RE
.PP
Patch:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Replace \fB\fCgem install binman \-\-development\fR tip in \fB\fCBinMan::conv()\fR with
\fB\fCgem install md2man\fR tip because the former just hangs in RubyGems 1.8.
.RE
.PP
Other:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Shorten markdown headings; improve documentation; clean up.
.RE
