.SH Version 3.0.0 (2012\-01\-09)
.PP
Major:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Removed the \fB\fCbinman/gemspec\fR helper library because it did not play well
with Bundler.  Use the standard \fB\fCadd_runtime_dependency\fR method instead.
This example
\[la]https://github.com/sunaku/md2man/commit/75d7a0064fa86f1c98dd01391ad82245fd387c20\[ra] shows what work is involved in upgrading.
.RE
.PP
Minor:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
The \fB\fCbinman/Rakefile\fR helper library now hooks into Bundler's Rake tasks.
Be sure to add the \fB\fCman/**/*\fR files to your gemspec accordingly
\[la]https://github.com/sunaku/md2man/commit/75d7a0064fa86f1c98dd01391ad82245fd387c20\[ra]\&.
.RE
.SH Version 2.0.0 (2011\-12\-06)
.PP
Major:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Removed the deprecated \fB\fCbinman/rake_tasks\fR helper library.  Use
\fB\fCbinman/rakefile\fR instead.
.RE
.PP
Patch:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Fixed infinite looping in the \fB\fCbinman/gemspec\fR helper library.
.RE
.PP
Other:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Upgraded to md2man v1 for Markdown to UNIX man page conversion.
.IP \(bu 2
Do not hard\-code the version number in \fB\fCbinman/gemspec\fR helper.
.RE
.SH Version 1.1.0 (2011\-11\-05)
.PP
Alert:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
The \fB\fCbinman/rake_tasks\fR library has been renamed (with deprecation) to
\fB\fCbinman/rakefile\fR\&.  The deprecation warning will be removed in the next
major release.
.RE
.PP
Minor:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Add \fB\fCbinman/gemspec\fR packaging convenience library which automatically
builds and includes your UNIX man page files in your gem packages and also
adds binman as a runtime and development gem dependency.
.RE
.SH Version 1.0.0 (2011\-10\-13)
.PP
Major:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
The \fB\fCBinMan::dump()\fR method and corresponding \fB\fCbinman dump\fR command now
extract the leading comment header from their input before returning the
markdown to roff conversion thereof.
.IP \(bu 2
The \fB\fCBinMan::read()\fR method and corresponding \fB\fCbinman read\fR command have
been renamed to \fB\fCBinMan::load()\fR and \fB\fCbinman load\fR respectively.
.RE
.PP
Minor:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Added \fB\fCBinMan::conv()\fR method and corresponding \fB\fCbinman conv\fR command to
encapsulate the markdown to roff conversion process.
.RE
.PP
Patch:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Pre\-built man pages included alongside a \fB\fCbin/\fR script were not displayed.
Instead, binman was (incorrectly) always trying to convert the leading
comment header from the \fB\fCbin/\fR script into a UNIX man page for display.
.RE
.PP
Other:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
README: explain dev deps and \fB\fCman/\fR dir packaging.
.RE
